patterns.title: FrumiBot Tech
response: /me I was written in September 2022 by @Frumious__Bandersnatch to add a little spice to @Jackie_Codes chat room. I initially understood commands !weather and !dice. I like saying hello to people in chat. I was inspired to make various responses when @SlaterUSA farts. Every now and then I like to remind people to move so their bodies don't atrophy. I am written in nodejs and make use of the OpenWeatherMap API.
